Class CreateMissionAtSettlementGoal

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FreeColObject>, ObjectWithId, GoalConstants

    public class CreateMissionAtSettlementGoal
extends Goal
    This Goal deals with one missionary unit. On construction, an AIUnit and an IndianSettlement are given to this. The Goal will try to create a mission at that settlement, eventually by bringing the missionary unit there first using a GotoAdjacentGoal. Should the target become invalid, the missionary will be given back to the parent of this goal (ManageMissionariesGoal, in most cases). Excess units will be given back to the parent, or the AIPlayer directly.
